│ violations, we need to ensure\n      // that we only use the optimized      │
│ operands when they are safe.\n      // \n      // For the instruction       │
│ building case (T = Value*), we can check if the\n      // operands are      │
│ instructions and whether they're the same as originals.\n      // For cost  │
│ estimation (T = InstructionCost), we don't create instructions\n      // so │
